<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٣١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4042">‌عَبْدِ الْمَلِكِ بْنِ عُمَيْرٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1520">‌حُصَيْنِ بْنِ أَبِي الْحُرِّ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2651">‌سَمُرَةَ بْنِ جُنْدُبٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ رَسُولُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«خَيْرُ مَا تَدَاوَيْتُمْ بِهِ الْحَجْمُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>